    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/c47a49d07ef897e98edf971c2c9cc773.avif?t=1762251140\" width=608 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>该演示展示了完整游戏的前两个关卡，并提供了 45 分钟的未来预览。您将体验基本机制和故事元素，引导您穿越哈迪斯的宫殿和许普诺斯的洞穴。该演示版包括所有核心机制，这些机制将在完整的游戏中进行扩展，增加额外的功能、关卡和区域。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/e312f60309e6d0bdd2602418e2d5a9d9.poster.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/e312f60309e6d0bdd2602418e2d5a9d9.webm?t=1762251140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/fc8b6ee2280b263c76bb030c7bb30d97.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为了离开地狱，你需要移动物体，使用重量和重力，并与平台互动来解锁门。每个级别都会带来独特的挑战，您必须解决这些挑战才能取得进步，将探索与解决谜题融为一体。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/c2e25b048a36c70e9395a832ce9bd175.poster.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/c2e25b048a36c70e9395a832ce9bd175.webm?t=1762251140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>                                             </strong></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/abac324dc6b6aed14d89e9858f6eff4d.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=100 /></span><i><strong> </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用控制自然生命周期的力量来解决你面前的难题和挑战。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/b8b993435032960f817f29935ffb248d.poster.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/b8b993435032960f817f29935ffb248d.webm?t=1762251140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/3b5f994729847a55713809201189f68c.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用闪电蘑菇的光芒暂时照亮你的道路，揭示隐藏的区域并引导你穿过阴暗的洞穴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/57f90217aa055a6ee1d693785a4a4d60.poster.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/57f90217aa055a6ee1d693785a4a4d60.webm?t=1762251140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/b932141810e211e8d248d9f3778f9597.avif?t=1762251140\" width=609 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对游戏像素和颜色进行自己的调整。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124820/extras/01b1da71daab5b77fd127aac1f613a6c.avif?t=1762251140\" width=608 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>        </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD - 运动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>空间 - 跳跃</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>E - 与物体的互动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人民币 - 手电筒</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>R - 旋转对象</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LMB - 施法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MMB - 投掷物体</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ScrollWheel - 更改手电筒颜色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TAB - 地图、库存、简介</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
